Those are the type of runes that are found rarely on monster or bosses they have yellow color
they also have random stats values when droping, they can be perfect or they have the minimun stats on them
They is also Chaos Rune having 5 word instead of 3, having the most power in them and unlocking some hero talent if not pick
only 1 chaos rune can be active and will reduce the amount of normal rune that can be use by 2

Those Runes will give bonus when keep in the Inventory, some of them will have terrible bonus as well
only 3 Runes can be active and are Unique and wont stack with other same Runes

Chaos Rune MotsX
Inteillgence Hero will have 25%-50% spell vamp on spell Q and W
Inteillgence Hero will have their Talent level 10 of their spell Q or W unlocking and having effect
Increase inteillgence by 10-25
Increase mana regeneration by 3.5-11
Increase mana by 100-600

Chaos Rune ToRxn
increase the damage of spell and basic attack on target that have 1 or less level difference from the hero level by 7% doesnt work on bosses
increase all stats by 4-12
increase spell amp by 2%-20%
increase damage VS Undead by 10%-15%
reduce base attack time with weapons by 0.10-0.20

Rune Poz
increase Primary stats by 1-4
increase Spell amp by 0.5%-1.6%
increase Spell Q damage by 1%-3%

Rune Alz
increase Agility by 1-10
increase Spell W damage by 5-15%
reduce health by 1-8%
reduce life regeneration by 3-5

Rune Los
Make Spell Q deal 0.1%-0.7% of current health in damage
Increase damage by 3-6
Increase attack speed by 3-9
reduce Inteillgence by 5-11
reduce Strenght by 2-5

Rune Deg
Make Ultimate Spell spell vamp by 5-10%
increase Primary stat by 2%-4%
increase spell amp by 0.5%-8%
Reduce attack speed by 4-12

Rune Zxl
Make Hero Passive that got Primary stats bonus increase by 3%-6%
increase damage by 1%-5%
increase spell amp by 1%-3.5%
reduce Base Attack time by 0.05-0.15 with all weapons

Rune Moj
increase attack speed by 1-25
increase strenght by 1-15
increase life by 50-300
increase mana by 10-250

Rune Oar
increase Primary stats by 2-4
increase armor by 1-3
increase magic resist by 3%-7%
increase Xp gain by 5%-10%

Rune Biw
increase spell amp by 1%-4%
increase mana regeneration by 1-3
